(722, 80, '1', 36, '1', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">To join the internet, the computer has to be connected to a _________</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;internet architecture board</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">internet society</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">internet service provider</span></p>', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">internet service provider</span></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 3, '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Answer: c</span><br style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Explanation: The ISPs (Internet Service Providers) are the main agents through which every computer is connected to the internet. They are licensed to allot public IP addresses to its customers in order to connect them to the internet.</span></p>', 1, '92', 92, 0, '', '1', 0),
