(1, 1, 'WELCOME TO A. S. ACADEMY', '<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: none; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><font size=\"3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">A. S. ACADEMY it has been running Under the Aegis of MSME Reg. with Govt. of India. A. S. ACADEMY is An ISO 9001 : 2008 Certified Institute, is a leading IT Education Provider Institution in India with strong presence in the state of Uttar Pradesh, Madhya Pradesh &amp; Maharashtra. In the present scenario where technology is playing pivotal role in dictating growth, there is a need for focused and specialized education to meet the ever changing to demands of industry A. S. ACADEMY is the right answer to that need.</font></em></span></strong></p>', '', 1, '1', '1', '1570605171395.png'),
