(4, 'FS1', '7', 'Diploma in Fire Safety', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:&#10;15.75pt;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">Course Code- FS1<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Duration- 12 Months<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Eligibility: 10<sup>th</sup><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-line-height-alt:&#10;15.75pt;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:red\">Diploma in Fire Safety</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;&#10;margin-left:.5in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal;&#10;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in;vertical-align:baseline\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.5pt;font-family:Wingdings;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;color:black;&#10;mso-themecolor:text1\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">&Oslash;<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">Safety of People in the event of Fire<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoN