i-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">2 - Arts &amp; Craft<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;&#10;margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:-16.1pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:left;&#10;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:16.1pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in;&#10;vertical-align:baseline\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;&#10;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;&#10;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">&middot;<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">3 - Arts File &amp; Plan Book<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;&#10;margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:-16.1pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:left;&#10;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:16.1pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in;&#10;vertical-align:baseline\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;&#10;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;&#10;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">&middot;<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">4 - Preparation of Teaching Aids<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;&#10;margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:-16.1pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:left;&#10;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:16.1pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in;&#10;vertical-align:baseline\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;&#10;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;&#10;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">&middot;<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">5 - Rhymes, Action Songs, Speech, Story<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;&#10;margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:-16.1pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:left;&#10;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:16.1pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in;&#10;vertical-align:baseline\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;&#10;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;&#10;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">&middot;<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">6 - Viva<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;&#10;margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:-16.1pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:left;&#10;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:16.1pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in;&#10;vertical-align:baseline\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;&#10;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;&#10;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">&middot;<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">7 - Internal Marks<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>', '', '1628320946629.jpg', '12', '9500', '', '1', '1', 1, 0, '400', '', '', '', 0),
(14, 'AS1', '10', 'Diploma In Acupressure', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;&#10;margin-left:-9.4pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;vertical-align:&#10;baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:red\">Diploma In acupressure</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;color:red\">Basic Acupressure Training &ndash; 1 (Chinese Acupressure) <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">Subjects: 1. What is acupressure? <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2. Concept of yin and yang. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3. Concept of physical and metaphysical. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4. Five element theory. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5. Organ clock <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6. Concept and definition of meridian. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 7. Fourteen Chinese meridians. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 8. Some important points &ndash; distal points, organ source point, xi-cleft points,<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; alarm points, &nbsp;&nbsp;emergency points, etc. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 9. Some important diseases and their treatment:&ndash; o Single point treatment o Multiple <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; point treatment <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 10. General precautions.<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;11. Solar plexus. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 12. Spinal column &amp; spinal cord. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 13. Correspondence system. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 14. Important body organs and their correspondence on palm &amp; sole. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 15. Treatment through correspondence. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.5in;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 16. Byol meridian chart. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;color:red\">Basic Acupressure Training &ndash; 2 (Electro Acupuncture) <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">Subjects: 1. Concept of Chinese meridians. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2. Concept of Electro Acupuncture According to Dr. Voll (EAV). <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3. Phases of diseases according to electro Acupuncture. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4. Important points of electro acupuncture:&ndash; o Measurement points o Control <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; measurement points o Reference points o Summation measurement points o Partial <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; summation measurement points o Autonomic innervation points o Lymphatic drainage <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; points<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5. Chinese meridians in view of electro acupuncture. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6. Eight tissue meridians of electro<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:13.7pt;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt;color:red\">acupuncture. Basic Acupressure Training &ndash; 3 (Ayurvedic Acupressure) <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:13.7pt;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">Subjects: 1. Concept of ayurveda &amp; ayurvedic acupressure <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:13.7pt;text-indent:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2. Samanya, vishesh <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:13.7pt;text-indent:.25in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3. Dravya, guna, karma<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:13.7pt;text-indent:22.3pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;4. Samavaya <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:13.7pt;text-indent:22.3pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5. Ten origin theory, plotting of ten origins on fingers joints <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:13.7pt;text-indent:22.3pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6. Ayurvedic shrots (meridians) &ndash; vertical, horizontal, spiral <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:13.7pt;text-indent:22.3pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 7. Mega meridians <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:13.7pt;text-indent:22.3pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 8. Plotting of organs on joints &amp; phalanges <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:13.7pt;text-indent:22.3pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 9. Treatment according to ayurvedic acupressure <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:13.7pt;text-indent:22.3pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 10. Ayurvedic bio-clock <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:13.7pt;text-indent:22.3pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 11. Treatment protocols specially on joints &amp; vertical meridians Basic <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;color:red\">Acupressure Training &ndash; 4 (Yogic Acupressure) <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">Subjects: 1. Concept of yogic acupressure. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2. Concept of chakras. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3. Definition of acu point, meridians and chakra. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4. Division of chakras:&ndash; o External chakras o Internal chakras o Regional chakras o Local<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; chakras <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5. Treatment through chakras. <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;&#10;margin-left:-9.4pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;vertical-align:&#10;baseline\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6. Treatment protocols.<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;&#10;margin-left:-9.4pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;vertical-align:&#10;baseline\"><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;&#10;mso-bidi-font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '1628323885344.jpg', '12', '6500', '', '1', '1', 1, 0, '800', '', '', '', 0),
