(28, 16, 'Ajay Kumar yadav, CCC (Grade-B)', 6, '', '162521639935.jpg', 0, 1, '<p><strong>&quot;It was a great experience studying at GSMT Institute, a memory to cherish for lifetime. If you want to make a career in Graphic Designing, E- Accounting &amp; CCC Computer Courses. I would highly recommend you to join <font color=\"#ff0000\">Gokulshree School Of Management And Technology Pvt Ltd</font>.&rdquo;</strong></p>'),
(31, 16, 'Sanjay Kumar Chaudhary, CCC(grade-B)', 4, '', '1625222725678.jpg', 0, 1, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>p&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Cabin, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">It was a great experience studying at GSMT Institute, a memory to cherish for lifetime. If you want to make a career in Graphic Designing, E- Accounting &amp; CCC Computer Courses. I would highly recommend you to join&nbsp;<font color=\"#ff0000\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none;\">Gokulshree School Of Management And Technology Pvt Ltd</font>.&rdquo;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>&nbsp;it.</strong></span></p>'),
(29, 16, 'Surendra Kumar Mishra, CCC (Grade-A)', 1, '', '1625220573908.jpeg', 0, 1, '<p>&nbsp;&quot;<strong>A very interesting and valuable experience.&nbsp; I learnt a lot and it gave me a good grounding in the basics. It really made me think, and I liked how it enabled me to interact wiht people through the practical work&quot;. I would highly recommend you to join Gokulshree School Of Management And Technology Pvt Ltd</strong><strong>&quot;.</strong></p>'),
