(59, 16, 'Ankit Kumar Mishra, ADCA (Grade-A+)', 0, '', '', 0, 1, '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Cabin, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">It was a great experience studying at GSMT Institute, a memory to cherish for lifetime. If you want to make a career in Graphic Designing, E- Accounting &amp; ADCA Computer Courses. I would highly recommend you to join&nbsp;<font color=\"#ff0000\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none;\">Gokulshree School Of Management And Technology Pvt Ltd</font>.&rdquo;</span></p>');
